    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Dependências de Gjs</bridgehead>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Exigida</bridgehead>
    <para role="required">
      <xref linkend="cairo"/>, <xref linkend="dbus"/>, <xref
linkend="gobject-introspection"/>, and <xref linkend="js102"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Recommended (required for GNOME)</bridgehead>
    <para role="recommended">
      <xref linkend="gtk3"/> and <xref linkend="gtk4"/>
    </para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect4">Opcionais</bridgehead>
    <para role="optional">
      <xref linkend="sysprof"/>, <xref linkend="valgrind"/> (for tests), <ulink
url="http://dtrace.org/blogs/about">DTrace</ulink>, <ulink
url="https://ltp.sourceforge.net/coverage/lcov.php">LCOV</ulink>, and <ulink
url="https://sourceware.org/systemtap">Systemtap</ulink>
    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Observações de Usuário(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/gjs"/>
    </para>
  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalação de Gjs</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>Gjs</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir gjs-build &amp;&amp;
cd    gjs-build &amp;&amp;

meson setup --prefix=/usr          \
            --buildtype=release    \
            --wrap-mode=nofallback \
            ..                     &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      <!-- https://github.com/mesonbuild/meson/issues/10577 -->
To test the results, issue: <command>ninja test</command>. The
<application>GTK</application> and <application>Cairo</application> tests
will fail if not running in an Xorg session.  Four tests are known to
timeout.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usuário(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

